---
title: "_setFeeAggregator (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_live: _whenNoLiveAuctions()
    q_check_live --> q_revert_live: liveAuctionExists
    q_revert_live --> q_error: revert LiveAuction()
    q_check_live --> q_check_zero: no live auctions
    q_check_zero --> q_revert_zero: feeAggregator == address(0)
    q_revert_zero --> q_error: revert InvalidZeroAddress()
    q_check_zero --> q_check_same: feeAggregator != address(0)
    q_check_same --> q_revert_same: s_feeAggregator == feeAggregator
    q_revert_same --> q_error: revert ValueNotUpdated()
    q_check_same --> q_check_interface: values differ
    q_check_interface --> q_revert_iface: feeAggregator != this AND !supportsInterface(IFeeAggregator)
    q_revert_iface --> q_error: revert InvalidFeeAggregator
    q_check_interface --> q_update: feeAggregator == this OR supportsInterface
    q_update --> [*]: s_feeAggregator = feeAggregator; emit FeeAggregatorSet

    note right of q_check_interface
        INV-014: Self-reference (address(this)) bypasses interface check - allows standalone mode
    end note

    q_error --> [*]
